            </svg>
          </span>
        </span>
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-[18px] leading-relaxed text-gray-400">
        CodeVetter is a desktop review cockpit for the diffs your agent
        ships. Catches 14 vulnerability classes — SQLi, PII leaks, CSRF,
        broken auth, and more — that Cursor, Claude Code, and Devin routinely miss.
        Runs entirely offline.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a
          href="#download"
          class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full sm:w-auto px-6 h-12 text-sm font-medium bg-white text-black hover:bg-gray-100 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,255,255,0.2)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(255,255,255,0.4)] transition-all duration-300 rounded-full"
        >
          <Icon name="download" class="w-4 h-4" width={16} height={16} strokeWidth={1.5} />
          Download for macOS
          <Icon
            name="arrow-right"
            class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"
            width={16}
            height={16}
            strokeWidth={1.5}
          />
        </a>
        <a
          href="#how"
          class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full sm:w-auto px-6 h-12 text-sm font-medium border border-white/20 text-white hover:border-white/40 hover:bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md transition-all duration-300 rounded-full"
        >
          <Icon name="terminal" class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-400" width={16} height={16} strokeWidth={1.5} />
          See it in action
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-7 gap-y-3 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[--color-text-mute]">
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[--color-ok]"></span>
          No telemetry
        </span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[--color-ok]"></span>
          Bring your own key
        </span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[--color-ok]"></span>
          Open source · ISC
        </span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[--color-ok]"></span>
          Signed binaries
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Hero preview cockpit — below LCP headline; defer layout/paint until near viewport. */}
    <div class="cv-hero-cockpit mt-20">
      <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div
          class="absolute -inset-x-12 -inset-y-10 blur-3xl pointer-events-none opacity-70"
          style="background: radial-gradient(60% 50% at 50% 30%, rgba(56,189,248,0.26), transparent 70%), radial-gradient(40% 40% at 80% 80%, rgba(167,139,250,0.22), transparent 70%);"
